{"tid":1480091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票] 咁嘅行為算唔算 <割𥱊•分化•指罵> ?","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:04:39.000Z","uid":131728,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3c62bc09348d482800602923e8af5c206f988b5b","tid":1480091,"uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:07:38.000Z","msg":"事件: 813個晚深夜，機場手足發現一名手持記者反光衣及懷疑拍攝示威者大頭近照，遭到質問，並被搜出內地護照、身份證及「我愛警察」藍色衫。其後經過多翻查問，該名男子亦無表露自己嘅記者身後。之後嘅事，我諗大家有留意都知道咩事。<br />\n<br />\n一開始，前線手足未有任何&rdquo;行動&rdquo;之前，有個朋友(A君)一路睇緊網上直播，一路係whatsapp group講: <br />\n&ldquo;假記者&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;扮記者&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;福建幫&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我唔明帶件藍衫做咩&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n跟住隔咗無耐, 當手足有所&rdquo;行動&rdquo;之後，A君係whatsapp group share咗條殘體字嘅link(內容係呢個男子係內地記者)，然後講:<br />\n&ldquo;打錯人la&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;DLLM&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;成班on9&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;仆街&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;Google都唔撚識(唔撚fc就郁手)&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n其他人聽到緊係火啦dllm, 咪即刻屌9佢<br />\nA君不但覺得自己無錯不得止，就屌翻人轉頭，話咁樣撚係分化割𥱊喎，想表達意見姐。<br />\n我表llm. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講真，坐係冷氣房做軍師有咩資格屌尻前線手足？<br />\n就算做錯咗，就諗方法點去補求，唔係一黎就屌尻人</span><br />\n<br />\n大家請投票，話俾A君知咁樣係唔係&lt;割𥱊&bull;分化&bull;指罵&gt;:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 係啦dllm 分化撚正仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唔係喎A君講得好啱喎做得好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 已unfriend"},{"pid":"57ffa65c1286013683d1332efa7fc72fffaaff84","tid":1480091,"uid":20283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 818要人呀 幫手推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c55eb8a68a35c37808b5cf1594aa1b73efd90236","tid":1480091,"uid":131728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgRtc6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgRtc6p.png&h=ad1bb769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分化撚正仆街"},{"pid":"05e5158739fea6c97ef4d41ed4f8abc51cb04269","tid":1480091,"uid":270871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"好多呢啲冷氣分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近期少咗，以前仲恐怖，逢親前線有嘢做啲人就會話係鬼嚟<br />\n又唔知咩事又要指指點點"},{"pid":"b355ef8559a466fc8f40c6a479cdd338fe0a0ea5","tid":1480091,"uid":131728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05e5158739fea6c97ef4d41ed4f8abc51cb04269","tid":1480091,"uid":270871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"好多呢啲冷氣分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近期少咗，以前仲恐怖，逢親前線有嘢做啲人就會話係鬼嚟<br />\n又唔知咩事又要指指點點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:14:42.000Z","msg":"分化完都算，話佢仲要覺得其他人係錯，死雞撐飯蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81ed646ab3d5b36ee80d5d06dc6152597e90133","tid":1480091,"uid":33152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"懷疑同樓主同一個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勿相認"},{"pid":"2abfe1e6a7786551a8a6078164cd6a8e01a06053","tid":1480091,"uid":131728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d81ed646ab3d5b36ee80d5d06dc6152597e90133","tid":1480091,"uid":33152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"懷疑同樓主同一個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勿相認"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"所有分化撚都係同一個老母生; 就係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab32229c03b6202ececb844d5bbab0c0a7ec7d5","tid":1480091,"uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"分化撚正仆街"},{"pid":"62a4ed0b1ac64db42e1ffea7511e83847a929e1d","tid":1480091,"uid":131728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"